title: The Killing of Freddie Gray – Episode 16 – Breakthroughs
description:
June 26, 2017 / The investigative binders provide fresh leads that break open some of the case’s mysteries. Also, a final look at Baltimore post-Freddie Gray.

Episode scoring music by AnimalWeapon, Blue Dot Sessions, Chris Zabriskie, Fleslit, H-LR, Jahzzar, Remain, Uncanny Valleys, VYVCH, and Sym5.

Thank you to our sponsors, WAG & Audible!

Wag! Is a must-have app for every dog owner. Get your first walk FREE by texting UNDISCLOSED to 25324 or by using the following link: https://app.adjust.com/xv8fal

Get a free audiobook with a 30 day trial today by signing up at www.audible.com/undisclosed.
